{"tid":2389140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★「狗狗幣」價格倍數急升　Robinhood 決定限制其交易","createTime":"2021-01-31T16:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7df79d06ed6e72c4282e14ca3df42b3227ee784e","tid":2389140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"最近美國股市投資氣氛變得相當熱烈，GME 的散戶大戰做空機構事件最近蔓延到加密貨幣，其中「狗狗幣」Dogecoin 價格因此倍數急升，而投資平台 Robinhood 就決定限制其交易嘗試降溫。<br />\n<br />\nGME 事件令不少投資者對於股市失去信心，開始將投資轉移到加密貨幣，Dogecoin 就成為了波幅最大的加密貨幣之一，在 24 小時內已經急升 3 倍，而且最高位接近 8 倍，猶如坐過山車。Robinhood 作為其中一個美國最普及的股票和加密貨幣投資平台，就表示「由於市場出現異常情況，已經暫時停止使用『即時購買力』資金購買加密貨幣，只可以用已結算資金購買，未來會繼續留意市場情況繼續與顧客溝通。」<br />\n<br />\nDogecoin 是在 2013 年開始流通，最初只是基於一個 meme 所開發的加密貨幣，並沒有什麼宏大的願景，但在幾年間一直都是最受歡迎的加密貨幣之一。而 Robinhood 之前因為限制用家購買 GME 股票，已經引起了 Google Play Store 劣評潮，但 Google 後來幫他們刪除了接近 10 萬個負評令用家更加不滿。今次事件會否再令不滿情況火上加油？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/31/robinhood-restricts-crypto-trading-as-bitcoin-dogecoin-surge/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F31%2Frobinhood-restricts-crypto-trading-as-bitcoin-dogecoin-surge%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1GzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=54072bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/31/robinhood-restricts-crypto-trading-as-bitcoin-dogecoin-surge/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"c21f86bccfaefafd7c1300e41c9e1a8e6dbbd006","tid":2389140,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a08db1eea28931caf717abc2c6bef140195289","tid":2389140,"uid":63669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"劫貧濟富<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba30fde54befe533a206e3f07abce7b2815955b5","tid":2389140,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87435757ea2c490d99f1ae71174151b61188066b","tid":2389140,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1a08db1eea28931caf717abc2c6bef140195289","tid":2389140,"uid":63669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"劫貧濟富<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"that's how the world work"},{"pid":"9a22799570f15fef2fbacd8748c7a62148de2754","tid":2389140,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe5370ca01ed3823dcee4415fca9a94febf6ef2","tid":2389140,"uid":266428,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"原來真係有dogecoin<br />\n以為musk係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88beed3f7777a8459234d60f2a2c226d34d588bf","tid":2389140,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"計劃經濟學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買乜要黨認可<br />\n<br />\nBTW 既然唔比升  咁點解要比佢上市? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}